          <li class="event ">
            <div class="event-date">
              <p>CADU executed the kick-off of the first development of the Long Island residential complex: York Homes.
                With this opening, CADU reaffirms its leadership in Quintana Roo and moves towards
                a more solid sales mix, thus increasing the middle-income segment participation in homes sold revenue.</p>
              <small>2017</small>
            </div>

          </li>
          <li class="event mover">
            <div class="event-date">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
