              <small>2015</small>
            </div>

          </li>
          <li class="event mover">
            <div class="event-date">

              <p>CADU carried out an Initial Public Offering on the Bolsa Mexicana de Valores (Mexican Stock Exchange)
                under the ticker symbol “CADU”, marking the return of the housing sector to the Mexican capital market
                after ten years.</p>

              <small>2015</small>
            </div>

          </li>

          <li class="event ">
            <div class="event-date">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <img src="/assets/cadu/images/content/cadu-bmv.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="CADU BMV">
