              <small>2007</small>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="event">
            <div class="event-date">
              <p>The institutionalization process of the Company starts.
              </p>
              <small>2006</small>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="event">
            <div class="event-date">
              <p>Start of operations in Quintana Roo with the “Villas Otoch I” development.</p>
              <small>2004</small>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="event ">
            <div class="event-date">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <img src="/assets/cadu/images/content/2004.png" class="img-responsive" alt="CADU">
