              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="event">
            <div class="event-date">
              <p>Start operations in Jalisco with the “Villas de Hacienda” development.</p>
              <small>2003</small>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="event">
            <div class="event-date">
